question: Question: Shirakawa discovered a class of these molecules that conduct electricity, and RAFT and ATRP are radical-mediated methods of creating them. For 10 points each: [10] Name these long molecules that consist of repeating units of a smaller molecule. Nylon and rayon are good examples.
